{
  "texts": [
    "The values represent the best among the two continual pretraining strategies of 'End-to-End' and 'Two-Stage'.",
    "The 'Overall' column represents the average value of Test Full, Difficult RS, Novel RS and Difficult SD.",
    "Vocabulary adaptation (best of MEDVOC-LLM and ScafFix) improves over BASE and CPT-only in 7 out of 8 overall settings.",
    "(Llama-2: 2; Llama-3.1: 2) out of eight high novelty settings.",
    "CPT-Only improves over BASE in 11 out of 16 higher OOV settings (Llama-2: 6; Llama-3.1: 5)."
  ]
}